OL,3,C'I've lost everything': Business owner
OL,4,Capplies for Uber licence after fire
OL,6,FA businessman whose four companies
OL,7,Fwere destroyed by a huge fire in
OL,8,FWolverhampton has told ITV News
OL,9,FCentral he is now applying for an Uber
OL,10,Flicence to cover his daily expenses.
OL,12,FThe blaze broke out at a factory
OL,13,Fbuilding on Sunbeam Street on 14
OL,14,FJanuary and could be seen for miles
OL,15,Faround.
OL,17,FRishi Garg told ITV News Central
OL,18,FBusiness Correspondent Mark Gough he
OL,19,Fis now facing an uncertain future.
