OL,3,C'I've lost everything': Business owner
OL,4,Capplies for Uber licence after fire
OL,6,FHe said: "We had a full business and
OL,7,Fnow everything is just gone," before
OL,8,Fadding: "I have two kids as well."
OL,10,FMr Garg and his business partner had
OL,11,Fworked together for six years and had
OL,12,Frecently moved all four of their
OL,13,Fbusinesses to the site.
OL,15,FHe said he is now trying to find
OL,16,Falternative ways to earn money to
OL,17,Fcover basic living costs.
