OL,3,C'I've lost everything': Business owner
OL,4,Capplies for Uber licence after fire
OL,6,F"I'm trying to apply for an Uber
OL,7,Flicence so I can cover my daily
OL,8,Fexpenses - that's all I can do at the
OL,9,Fmoment." he said.
OL,11,FThe fire has also meant Mr Garg has
OL,12,Fhad to lay off nine members of staff.
OL,14,FHe told ITV News Central: "Right now,
OL,15,FI can't afford to pay my mortgage, so
OL,16,Fhow can I pay their salaries?"
OL,18,FMr Garg and his business partner had
OL,19,Finvested around #500,000 into one of
OL,20,Fthe businesses, including specialist
OL,21,Fmachinery.
