OL,6,FHe said: "This is the first machine
OL,7,Flike this in the UK", before adding:
OL,8,F"I spent around #70,000 on it, and
OL,9,Fthen there were the accessories and
OL,10,Fset-up costs on top of that."
OL,12,FWest Midlands Fire Service said
OL,13,Ffirefighters have identified a
OL,14,Fpossible area where the fire started,
OL,15,Fbut the site remains too dangerous to
OL,16,Ffully access.
OL,18,FThe cause of the fire is currently
OL,19,Fundetermined.
